HEADWORD: Wasting
<hw>Wast"ing</hw>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Causing waste; also, undergoing
waste; diminishing; <as>as, a <ex>wasting</ex> disease; a
<ex>wasting</ex> fortune.</as></def> <-- wasting asset = 2nd sense.
Should be separate senses. -->⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

